        {
            "id": 6428326,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 拼多多控股(PDD-US)大跌5.03%，報98.96美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>拼多多控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PDD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PDD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PDD-US</a>)截至台北時間22日03:43股價下跌5.24美元，報98.96美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量9,286,767（股），盤中最高價103.78美元、最低價98.93美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.63%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.65%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.73%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.16%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>拼多多控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PDD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PDD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PDD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.37%</li> <li>近 1 月：+8.33%</li> <li>近 3 月：-0.25%</li> <li>近 6 月：-20.8%</li> <li>今年以來：-8.1%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6428326",
